#. type: Title ==
#: upstream/_posts/2014-04-11-infinispan-security-1-authorization.adoc:74
#, no-wrap, fuzzy
msgid "Obtaining a Subject"
msgstr "件名の取得"

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_posts/2014-04-11-infinispan-security-1-authorization.adoc:90
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Infinispan is not fussy about how you obtain a JAAS http://docs.oracle.com/"
"javase/7/docs/api/javax/security/auth/Subject.html[Subject]: you may use "
"your container's features, or a third-party library (such as https://www."
"jboss.org/picketbox[JBoss PicketBox] or https://shiro.apache.org/[Apache "
"Shiro]). The important thing is that your Subject should be populated with a "
"set of http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/security/Principal."
"html[Principals] which represent the user and the groups it belongs to in "
"your security domain (e.g. LDAP, Active Directory, etc).  It is then the "
"duty of the _mapper_ to look through the principals associated with the "
"Subject and convert them into roles suitable for matching those you have "
"defined at the container level.  Once you have a Subject, you interact with "
"the Cache within the context of a _PrivilegedAction_ as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Infinispan は、JAAS link:http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/javax/"
"security/auth/Subject.html[Subject の] "
"取得方法にこだわることはありません。コンテナの機能を使用してもよいし、サードパーティのライブラリ ( link:https://www.jboss."
"org/picketbox[JBoss PicketBox] や link:https://shiro.apache.org/[Apache "
"Shiro] など) を使用してもよいでしょう。重要なことは、サブジェクトには、セキュリティドメイン(LDAP、Active "
"Directoryなど)内のユーザとそのユーザが所属するグループを表す link:http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/"
"docs/api/java/security/Principal.html[プリンシパル] "
"のセットが含まれている必要があるということです。次に、サブジェクトに関連付けられたプリンシパルを調べて、コンテナレベルで定義したものと一致するのに適したロールに変換するのが "
"_マッパー_ の役目です。サブジェクトを取得したら、次のように、 _PrivilegedAction の_ コンテキスト内で Cache と対話します。"

